OL,3,C'No breach of planning control' Wigan
OL,4,CCouncil refuse stop notice on
OL,5,Cwarehouses
OL,7,FWigan Council has turned down a 'stop
OL,8,Fnotice' issued over a large warehouse
OL,9,Fproject being built in Greater
OL,10,FManchester.
OL,12,FThe Astley Warehouse Action Group
OL,13,Fargue that the 18-metre warehouses at
OL,14,Fthe back of the Henfold Estate should
OL,15,Fnever legally have been built.
OL,17,FThe buildings have been described by
OL,18,Fresidents as 'like a cruise ship in
OL,19,Four back garden' as they block out
OL,20,Flight and tower above the houses and a
OL,21,Fnearby Primary School.
