OL,7,FResidents have complained about
OL,8,Fbreathing difficulties and health
OL,9,Fconditions they believe are linked to
OL,10,Fthe building work.
OL,12,FOne resident, Paula Boardman says the
OL,13,Fongoing work so close to her home is
OL,14,Fdamaging her property :"We've actually
OL,15,Ffound big cracks in the side of the
OL,16,Fproperty, which is actually everyday
OL,17,Fgetting worse and a lot bigger."
