OL,3,C'No breach of planning control' Wigan
OL,4,CCouncil refuse stop notice on
OL,5,Cwarehouses
OL,7,FThe Stop Notice was submitted on
OL,8,FThursday 13 November in the hope that
OL,9,Fa halt could be put on the work while
OL,10,Fan independent audit took place.
OL,12,FWigan Council said in a letter to the
OL,13,FAction Group: "Following a thorough
OL,14,Freview of all of the issues raised and
OL,15,Freceipt of legal advice, the Council's
OL,16,Fclear conclusion is that there is no
OL,17,Flegal basis to enact such a request,
OL,18,Fas there has been no breach of
OL,19,Fplanning control."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
