OL,7,F"In these circumstances if we were to
OL,8,Fissue one, we would be acting
OL,9,Funlawfully, and at risk of incurring
OL,10,Fsignificant adverse costs to the
OL,11,Ftaxpayer."
OL,13,FThe Action Group has reacted angrily
OL,14,Fto Council's refusal to issue a stop
OL,15,Fnotice, saying it has "avoiding the
OL,16,Fmost serious evidence"
