OL,7,FA spokesperson for the Action Group
OL,8,Fsaid: "We issued a well-researched,
OL,9,Fdetailed Stop Notice Request backed by
OL,10,Fall political parties. It has taken
OL,11,Feight days to receive a response - and
OL,12,Fnot one of our core issues has been
OL,13,Faddressed."
OL,15,F"The Council must now explain why they
OL,16,Fapproved a development reliant on
OL,17,Fmitigation that cannot be delivered,
OL,18,Fwhy residents were not re-consulted on
OL,19,Fmajor changes, and why the drainage
OL,20,Fplans do not reflect the actual
OL,21,Fdevelopment being built."
