OL,7,FThe group has now written back to
OL,8,FWigan Council demanding direct answers
OL,9,Fand calling for construction to be
OL,10,Fpaused while the evidence is properly
OL,11,Freviewed.
OL,13,FThey are also asking the Council to
OL,14,Fcommission a retrospective
OL,15,FEnvironmental Impact Assessment (EIA)
OL,16,Fand Landscape and Visual Impact
OL,17,FAssessment (LVIA), given the reliance
OL,18,Fon mitigation that is no longer
OL,19,Fachievable.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
