OL,3,C'No breach of planning control' Wigan
OL,4,CCouncil refuse stop notice on
OL,5,Cwarehouses
OL,7,FThe Council said:" We are confident
OL,8,Fthat the decision to grant planning
OL,9,Fpermission aligns with national
OL,10,Fplanning policy.
OL,12,F"Nonetheless we fully acknowledge the
OL,13,Fconcerns being raised and we have
OL,14,Fcommitted to carrying out an
OL,15,Findependent audit of the planning
OL,16,Fprocess to ensure additional
OL,17,Ftransparency.
OL,19,F"We will remain in dialogue with the
OL,20,Fgroup as that progresses."
